metadata.name: World of Waves - #1
metadata.description:
Photography published in National Geographic Your Shot in April 2019 and awarded the story cover-photo position.   

Photograph curated and selected by a Senior Producer at National Geographic on assignment.

North facing photograph capturing the Pacific Ocean on the Nicoya Peninsula in Costa Rica.   One of only five "Blue Zones" on planet earth.

- 1/1 edition
- Ocean photography
- Pacific ocean
- 120+ Megapixels
- Photographer: ChadwickNFT

*See collection details for ownership / collector utility .
